THEY WOULD STILL FEEL
COMPELLED TO BATHE.

00:48:48.100 --> 00:48:51.830
TRANSLATOR: FOR THEM, THE
GANGES IS THE MEDIUM OF LIFE.

00:48:51.830 --> 00:48:54.630
JUST LIKE A FISH CANNOT
BE SEPARATED FROM WATER,

00:48:54.630 --> 00:48:59.500
