00:49:09.200 --> 00:49:12.660
TRANSLATOR: IF I SIT WITH
THE MASSES AND SAY THAT

00:49:12.660 --> 00:49:16.330
THE GANGES HAS BECOME
DIRTY, IS POLLUTED,

00:49:16.330 --> 00:49:20.160
WITHIN A MINUTE OR TWO
SOMEONE WILL GET UP AND SAY,

00:49:20.160 --> 00:49:24.330
"YOUR HOLINESS,
PLEASE DON'T SAY THAT.

00:49:24.330 --> 00:49:27.760
IT'S UNBEARABLE.
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

00:49:27.760 --> 00:49:32.200
CAN THE MOTHER EVER
