00:49:32.200 --> 00:49:35.860
BUT WHEN YOU SHOW THEM
WHAT'S HAPPENING THEY SAY,

00:49:35.860 --> 00:49:38.630
"NO, THE CITY'S SEWAGE
AND DRAINS SHOULD NOT BE

00:49:38.630 --> 00:49:42.000
EMPTIED INTO THE RIVER.
