00:49:42.000 --> 00:49:44.530
IF THIS LOVE AND RESPECT FOR
THE RIVER CAN BE HARNESSED

00:49:44.530 --> 00:49:46.930
IT CAN BECOME
A GREAT POWER

00:49:46.930 --> 00:49:50.400
WHICH CAN HELP US
IN SO MANY WAYS.

00:49:50.400 --> 00:49:53.660
>>IF THE POWER OF LOVE
CAN TRULY SAVE THIS RIVER

00:49:53.660 --> 00:49:56.200
THEN THERE IS HOPE YET.

00:49:56.200 --> 00:49:59.330
FOR NO RIVER ON EARTH
IS AS LOVED BY ITS PEOPLE

00:49:59.330 --> 00:50:03.100
AS THE GANGES.

00:50:03.100 --> 00:50:07.800
PERHAPS 4,000 YEARS OF FAITH
IN THE PURITY OF THESE WATERS

00:50:07.800 --> 00:50:12.560
WILL UNDO THE LAST
50 YEARS OF NEGLECT.

00:50:12.560 --> 00:50:17.730
BUT POLLUTION IS JUST ONE OF
THE PROBLEMS TO BE FACED.

00:50:17.730 --> 00:50:23.730
AS THE GLACIER WHICH FEEDS
THE RIVER CONTINUES TO RECEDE

00:50:23.730 --> 00:50:26.030
THERE IS A REAL
DANGER THAT THE

00:50:26.030 --> 00:50:30.100
SOURCE OF THE
GANGES WILL DISAPPEAR.

00:50:30.100 --> 00:50:35.460
YET INDIA NEEDS THE RIVER
TODAY MORE THAN EVER.

00:50:35.460 --> 00:50:38.730
AS THE POPULATION BOOM
CONTINUES, THE AMOUNT OF WATER

00:50:38.730 --> 00:50:43.330
AVAILABLE TO EACH PERSON
IS RAPIDLY DECREASING.

00:50:43.330 --> 00:50:47.330
IT'S ESTIMATED THAT BY 2020
INDIA'S DEMAND FOR WATER

00:50:47.330 --> 00:50:51.360
WILL EXCEED ALL
SOURCES OF SUPPLY.

00:50:51.360 --> 00:50:55.660
DRASTIC CHANGE IS
NEEDED TO SAVE THE RIVER

00:50:55.660 --> 00:50:59.800
AND PROTECT THE
FUTURE OF HER PEOPLE.

00:50:59.800 --> 00:51:05.800
HOW THAT CAN BE DONE IS THE
CHALLENGE FACING INDIA TODAY.